snippet.title: Diana and Roma - a new school story about Hobbies
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma play school. Children talk about their hobbies and interests. Roma loves to play football and Diana loves to draw. And what is your hobby? What do you like to do? What is fun for you?
Thanks for watching!
